column5: not sure if to head up there this weekend, anybody have a report on the conditions? thanks Chris
~~~~Check in with Terry up at Eagle Lake Adventures, in West Gilford at 1-705-754-1637, he'll let you know whats happening up in that area
Small lakes will be fine.  I was in the Tory Hill area over a week ago on about 3", and there's been plenty of cold temps since then.
Thats excellent news. Heading up that way this weekend for a wee brookie bonanza!!!! Anyone been out in the Highlands? I got bets on limits if anyone is willing to take the wager????
talked to a buddy..ice is fine on small lakes..caution as always first of the year...fishing = awesome. EATING GOOD TOMMORROW!!!!!
